	<Fixlet>
		<Title>MS03-002: Cumulative Patch for Microsoft Content Management Server</Title>
		<Description><![CDATA[
Microsoft has released a security rollup package eliminating a new vulnerability in Microsoft Content Management Server 2001 (MCMS), including all old vulnerabilities for MCMS. The new vulnerability allows a malicious user to use a script on the victim's computer by embedding the script into a link to a site generated by MCMS. When the page is generated by MCMS, the script will be incorporated into the page. This could result in an attacker being able to access information the user shared with the legitimate site. After downloading and installing the security rollup package, affected machines will no longer be susceptible to this vulnerability. <BR><b><BR>Note:</b> This patch requires a local administrator present at the client computer to complete the installation manually.<BR><BR><b>Note:</b> Microsoft has announced that this patch will be included in Content Management Server 2001 Service Pack 2. <BR><BR><b>File Size: </b>1.43 MB<BR><BR><b>Note:</b> This Fixlet message does not have a default action. For more information on default actions, see BigFix KB #474.
]]></Description>
		<Relevance>(if( name of operating system starts with "Win" ) then platform id of operating system != 3 else false) AND (if exists property "in proxy agent context" then ( not in proxy agent context ) else true )</Relevance>
		<Relevance>(language of version block of file "kernel32.dll" of system folder contains "English") OR (exists value of key "HKLM\System\CurrentControlSet\Control\Nls\MUILanguages" of registry)</Relevance>
		<Relevance>not exists key "HKLM\Software\Wow6432Node\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion" whose (exists value "ProductId" of it OR exists value "CommonFilesDir" of it) of registry AND not exists values "PROCESSOR_ARCHITECTURE" whose (it as string as lowercase = "ia64") of keys "HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Session Manager\Environment" of registry</Relevance>
		<Relevance>(exists key "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\NCompass\Resolution Content Server" of registry)</Relevance>
		<Relevance>(value "Patches" of key "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\NCompass\Resolution Content Server\VersionInfo" of registry as string contains "SP1")</Relevance>
		<Relevance>(not exist key "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Updates\MCMS 2001\810487" of registry)</Relevance>
